### Document Management API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v1
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### ==============================================
### 1. Upload Document
### ==============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Sample Contract Document
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

This is a sample contract for testing purposes
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="document"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### ==============================================
### 2. List Documents (with pagination)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents?page=1&limit=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 3. List Documents (with filters)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents?status=UPLOADED&search=contract
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 4. Get Document by ID
### ==============================================
@documentId = DOCUMENT_ID_HERE
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/{{documentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 5. Update Document Metadata
### ==============================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/documents/{{documentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Contract Title",
  "description": "Updated description for the contract"
}

### ==============================================
### 6. Get User Document Statistics
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 7. Download Document (Original)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/{{documentId}}/download?version=original
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 8. Download Document (Signed)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/{{documentId}}/download?version=signed
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 9. Delete Document
### ==============================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/{{documentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### CURL Examples
### ==============================================

# Upload Document
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/documents \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#   -F "document=@./sample.pdf" \
#   -F "title=Sample Contract" \
#   -F "description=Test document"

# List Documents
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/documents?page=1&limit=10" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"

# Get Document
# curl -X GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/documents/DOCUMENT_ID \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"

# Update Document
# curl -X PATCH http://localhost:5001/api/v1/documents/DOCUMENT_ID \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"title":"Updated Title"}'

# Download Document
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/documents/DOCUMENT_ID/download?version=original" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#   -o document.pdf

# Delete Document
# curl -X DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/v1/documents/DOCUMENT_ID \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"
